Wheelchair basketball has found a state-of-the-art sports facility in Cape Town to play in. #eNCA Courtesy #DStv403 CAPE TOWN - Wheelchair basketball has found a state-of-the-art sports facility in Cape Town to play in. Called Battery Park, it caters to both players with disabilities, as well as able-bodied players. Teams are currently trying out the courts for the first time in the annual Premier Club Championship League. Watch the video above for more details on this story